arts.ttl: 'This is what contenders do!' | Coventry's incredible comeback over West Brom
arts.sum: Highlights from the Sky Bet Championship game between Coventry City and West Bromwich Albion.

arts.ttl: Coventry hit back to beat 10-player West Brom in thriller
arts.sum: Championship leaders Coventry came from two goals behind to beat 10-man West Brom 3-2 in a thriller at the CBS Arena.
